WEBVTT

00:00:28.553 --> 00:00:32.045
Because AI operates
just like bureaucracies.

00:00:32.403 --> 00:00:34.815
The essence of bureaucracy

00:00:34.839 --> 00:00:39.283
is to favor rules and procedures
over human judgment.

00:00:39.887 --> 00:00:43.728
And AI decides solely based on rules.

00:00:44.062 --> 00:00:46.895
Many rules inferred from past data

00:00:46.919 --> 00:00:48.823
but only rules.

00:00:49.204 --> 00:00:52.934
And if human judgment
is not kept in the loop,

00:00:52.958 --> 00:00:57.514
AI will bring a terrifying form
of new bureaucracy --

00:00:57.538 --> 00:01:00.537
I call it "algocracy" --